2527258\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104epv1665703523533.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epv1665703523533.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epv1665703523533.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"epv1665703523533\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Add watches from the debugger main window or from the browser.</p>\n<section class=\"section ul\" id=\"epv1665703523533__section_N1001A_N10017_N10001\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53399e1_d53400e1_d53401e1\">To set watches on ProcScript functions, fields, and component variables:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53402e1_d53403e1_d53404e1\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View</span><abbr title=\"and then\"> &gt; </abbr><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Select Watches</span></span>. <p class=\"p\" id=\"epv1665703523533__p_d175337e1_d175338e1_d175339e1\">If the debugger is not\n                        in control, this menu item is unavailable.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53405e1_d53406e1_d53407e1\">Select <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Scope</span> and\n                     type of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Function</span> to determine the list of\n                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable Watches</span>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53408e1_d53409e1_d53410e1\">In the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable\n                        Watches</span> list, select the items to watch and click the\n                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Add</span> icon. <p class=\"p\" id=\"epv1665703523533__p_d175340e1_d175341e1_d175342e1\">To\n                        select multiple items, use <span class=\"keyword\">Ctrl+Click</span> and\n                           <span class=\"keyword\">Shift-Click</span>. You can also use the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Select\n                           All</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Deselect All</span> icons to select\n                        and clear all items.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53411e1_d53412e1_d53413e1\">To set a watch on an expression:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53414e1_d53415e1_d53416e1\">From the debugger, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View</span><abbr title=\"and then\"> &gt; </abbr><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Quick Watch</span></span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53417e1_d53418e1_d53419e1\">Enter an expression and click\n                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Add Watch</span>. <p class=\"p\" id=\"epv1665703523533__p_d175343e1_d175344e1_d175345e1\">The expression is added to the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Watches</span> pane.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53420e1_d53421e1_d53422e1\">To set a watch on a field or variable from the\n               browser, highlight the field or variable in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Structure</span>\n               pane, right-click, and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Add Watch</span>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53423e1_d53424e1_d53425e1\">To remove a watch, in the\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Watches</span> pane of the debugger, select the watched item,\n               right-click, and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Remove</span>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epv1665703523533__li_d53426e1_d53427e1_d53428e1\">To save the current list of watches, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View </span><abbr title=\"and then\"> &gt; </abbr><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Preferences</span></span>. and click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Save</span>. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yys1665703523614.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProcScript expressions</a><p>View valid ProcScript expression values.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527258\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527258\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Working with watches Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Add watches from the debugger main window or from the browser. To set watches on ProcScript functions, fields, and component variables: Choose View > Select Watches . If the debugger is not in control, this menu item is unavailable. Select Scope and type of Function to determine the list of Selectable Watches . In the Selectable Watches list, select the items to watch and click the Add icon. To select multiple items, use Ctrl+Click and Shift-Click . You can also use the Select All and Deselect All icons to select and clear all items. To set a watch on an expression: From the debugger, choose View > Quick Watch . Enter an expression and click Add Watch . The expression is added to the Watches pane. To set a watch on a field or variable from the browser, highlight the field or variable in the Structure pane, right-click, and choose Add Watch . To remove a watch, in the Watches pane of the debugger, select the watched item, right-click, and choose Remove . To save the current list of watches, choose View > Preferences . and click Save . Related Links ProcScript expressions View valid ProcScript expression values. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}